    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;illusion&nbsp;(figment)&nbsp;[mind-affecting];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;alchemist 2, bard 3, medium 2, mesmerist 3, psychic 3, sorcerer/wizard 3, witch 2;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 minute<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;you or one gnome touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;see text<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;none;&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions as the <i>dream</i> spell, except as follows. The messenger must be yourself or a gnome touched. The message can be no longer than 20 words. If the recipient of the message is not asleep when the spell is cast, the spell automatically fails.</p>\n</div>\n"
